(62, 1, '2016-03-13 01:38:32', '2016-03-13 01:38:32', '<div class="row">\r\n<div class="col-md-4 col-sm-12"><a href="#"><img class="img-responsive wow slideInLeft" src="http://www.beta.ubtiinc.com/content/uploads/2015/07/industry-aerospace.jpg" alt="" /></a></div>\r\n<div class="col-md-8 col-sm-12 wow slideInRight">\r\n<h2><a href="#">Aerospace &amp; Defense</a></h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><a href="#">In the aerospace industry, UBTI is known for consistently exceeding the stringent requirements demanded of IT solution providers. We develop state-of-the-art mission-critical software and business intelligence solutions geared to the industry’s high performance needs. We focus on efficient integrated design, ironclad system security, flexible yet robust platforms and processes, intuitive interfaces, and world-class software development services. From requirements gathering, design and development to user acceptance testing, we ensure that your IT initiatives are delivered per specifications, on schedule and on budget Test..</a></p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="row">\r\n<div class="col-md-4 col-sm-12"><a href="#"><img class="img-responsive wow slideInLeft" src="http://www.beta.ubtiinc.com/content/uploads/2015/07/industry-finance.jpg" alt="" /></a></div>\r\n<div class="col-md-8 col-sm-12 wow slideInRight">\r\n<h2><a href="#">Financial Services</a></h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><a href="#">UBTI draws on our deep experience within the financial services industry to help institutions find innovative ways to optimize processes, reduce back office costs, manage risk, build customer loyalty, and plan for evolving competitive and regulatory landscapes. We offer end-to-end services and products that will give you the edge you need to make informed decisions.</a></p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="row">\r\n<div class="col-md-4 col-sm-12"><a href="#"><img class="img-responsive wow slideInLeft" src="http://www.beta.ubtiinc.com/content/uploads/2015/07/industry-healthcare.jpg" alt="" /></a></div>\r\n<div class="col-md-8 col-sm-12 wow slideInRight">\r\n<h2><a href="#">Healthcare</a></h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><a href="#">UBTI provides economical and efficient technology solutions built for your increasingly complex environment. Our experienced Healthcare Professional Services team provide consulting and software development services that enable MSOs, ACOs, IPAs, medical groups, health plan organizations, and healthcare providers to perform at the highest levels. We are able to rapidly customize and integrate reliable healthcare software modules, extend your current applications and optimize native reporting capabilities to accelerate implementations and lower costs. This innovative, low-risk and yet efficient approach allows for flexibility and delivers significant cost savings.</a></p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="row">\r\n<div class="col-md-4 col-sm-12"><a href="#"><img class="img-responsive wow slideInLeft" src="http://www.beta.ubtiinc.com/content/uploads/2015/07/industry-healthcare.jpg" alt="" /></a></div>\r\n<div class="col-md-8 col-sm-12 wow slideInRight">\r\n<h2><a href="#">OTHER INDUSTRIES</a></h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><a href="#">UBTI has been making software smarter and more efficient for more than two decades, providing businesses with better visibility and access to their data. Our technology experts are available to deliver end-to-end solutions, or supplement internal resources on a project basis. We offer affordable, top-notch support whether we are working from our offices or yours.</a></p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Industries', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'industries', '', '', '2016-11-07 14:11:20', '2016-11-07 14:11:20', '', 0, 'http://ubti/industries/', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(65, 1, '2015-07-27 01:38:32', '2015-07-27 01:38:32', ' <div class="strip"> manufacturing <img src="http://ubti.brmdevsite.com/content/uploads/2016/10/dot11.png" /> supply chain </div>\r\n\r\n<img class="img-responsive" src="http://ubti.brmdevsite.com/content/uploads/2016/11/img3.png" width="100%" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Aerospace Supply Chain Management Software</strong>\r\n\r\nUBTI’s reputation for aerospace software development is unrivaled, earning numerous customer awards and accolades from top-tier organizations in the aerospace industry for our best-in-class custom software solutions.\r\n\r\nWe consistently exceed the stringent requirements aerospace and defense organizations place on their IT solution providers. We develop state-of-the-art, mission-critical software and business intelligence solutions geared to this industry’s high-performance needs. Our focus is on efficient, integrated design; ironclad system security with flexible yet robust platforms and processes; intuitive interfaces; and world-class software development services. From requirement gathering, design, and development to user acceptance testing, we ensure that your IT initiatives are delivered on spec, on schedule and on budget.\r\n\r\n<strong>Capstone Performance Visibility Suite</strong>\r\n\r\nIn addition to custom software development, UBTI offers the Capstone™ suite of sophisticated supply chain software modules designed to automatically monitor all essential components of service and material delivery, regulatory compliance, and quality control.\r\n\r\n<strong>Superior Approach</strong>\r\n\r\nUBTI conducts intensive, expert peer reviews of customer projects that expand the universe of viable alternatives to assure the best possible solution is ultimately delivered within a cost-effective development plan. This complete vetting process fuels innovation and elevates quality.\r\n\r\nWith visually rich dashboards displaying key indicator data from our full-featured information management systems, we offer aerospace companies a superior approach to proactively managing processes while infusing high quality and significant efficiencies across the enterprise.\r\n\r\n<strong>How can we help?</strong>\r\n\r\nUBTI’s Aerospace Professional Services Practice is exceptionally qualified to take on your next custom software development project, due to our:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Supremely capable team of aerospace software development experts who are well-versed in best practices</li>\r\n 	<li>Proprietary pre-built software modules created specifically for the aerospace industry to accelerate the software build and save on costs</li>\r\n 	<li>More than a decade of experience immersed in developing custom software applications for the aerospace industry, with unparalleled expertise in technology\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><span style="line-height: 1.5;">Conversion of legacy platforms to web</span></li>\r\n 	<li>Workflow management</li>\r\n 	<li>Program management</li>\r\n 	<li>Business intelligence and executive dashboards</li>\r\n 	<li>Smart integration across enterprise information silos</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Contact us today to <a href="#" style="text-decoration: underline;" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#myModal">learn more.</a></p>', 'Aerospace', 'In aerospace and defense, UBTI is well known for consistently exceeding the stringent requirements this industry demands of IT solution providers. We develop state-of-the-art mission-critical software and business intelligence solutions geared to the industry’s high performance needs. We focus on efficient integrated design, ironclad system security, flexible yet robust platforms and processes, intuitive interfaces, and world-class software development services. From requirements gathering, design, and development to user acceptance testing, we ensure that your IT initiatives are delivered on spec, on schedule, and on budget.', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'aerospace-and-defense', '', '', '2016-11-28 13:37:45', '2016-11-28 13:37:45', '', 62, 'http://ubti/areospace-and-defence/', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(66, 1, '2015-07-27 01:38:32', '2015-07-27 01:38:32', '<div class="strip"> asset management <img src="http://ubti.brmdevsite.com/content/uploads/2016/10/dot11.png" /> banking </div>\r\n\r\n<img class="img-responsive" src="http://ubti.brmdevsite.com/content/uploads/2016/11/img2.png" width="100%" />\r\n\r\nAsset management firms thrive on data, and the faster they get it the better. UBTI has 20 years’ experience integrating and enhancing existing systems so our customers can see the information they need, when they need it. We are experts at integrating: \r\n\r\n\r\n<div class="fin">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li style="list-style:none;"><strong><img src="http://ubti.brmdevsite.com/content/uploads/2016/10/tick.png" />Order Management Systems</strong> – Charles River Development / Linedata / Longview</li>\r\n<li style="list-style:none;"><strong><img src="http://ubti.brmdevsite.com/content/uploads/2016/10/tick.png" />Data Providers</strong> – Bloomberg / Markit / TREPP / INTEX / FACTSET / RIMES / Freddie Mac / Fannie Mae / Ginnie Mae</li>\r\n<li style="list-style:none;"><strong><img src="http://ubti.brmdevsite.com/content/uploads/2016/10/tick.png" />Pricing</strong> – Bloomberg / Markit / IDC</li>\r\n<li style="list-style:none;"><strong><img src="http://ubti.brmdevsite.com/content/uploads/2016/10/tick.png" />Portfolio / Fund Accounting Systems</strong> – Mellon / Advent</li>\r\n<li style="list-style:none;"><strong><img src="http://ubti.brmdevsite.com/content/uploads/2016/10/tick.png" />Rating</strong> – S&P / Moody / Fitch</li>\r\n<li style="list-style:none;"><strong><img src="http://ubti.brmdevsite.com/content/uploads/2016/10/tick.png" />Customer Relation Management</strong> – Microsoft / Salesforce / Aptean / Saratoga</li>\r\n<li style="list-style:none;"><strong><img src="http://ubti.brmdevsite.com/content/uploads/2016/10/tick.png" />Analytic Services</strong> – 1010data</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\nUBTI’s Enterprise Data Management (EDM) funnels data from various sources into a centralized data repository. Our approach ensures effective data governance, data quality, data profiling and security, backed by round-the-clock production and maintenance support.\r\n\r\nOur <a href="http://ubti.brmdevsite.com/solutions/financial-reporting-and-analytics-solution/" style="text-decoration:underline;">Financial Reporting & Analytics System (FRAS) framework</a> provides users with role-based visibility into the portfolio, performance, and risk exposure, allowing for efficient analysis of complex information.\r\nThis streamlined data empowers firms to spend more time on what matters most: managing risk, maintaining compliance, reducing expenses, and focusing on customers.\r\n\r\n<p><strong>EFFICIENTLY GENERATE REPORTS</strong></p>\r\n\r\nIt can be challenging to keep up with reporting requirements due to increasing demand, resulting in an increasing backlog and longer turnaround time. UBTI’s integration services enable you to quickly generate reports for compliance and portfolio analytics, with all of your data conveniently in one place.\r\n\r\n<p style="padding:0px; margin:0px;"><img class="img-responsive" src="http://ubti.brmdevsite.com/content/uploads/2016/11/reporting1.png" width="100%" /></p>\r\n<p style="font-style:italic;">UBTI syncs multiple data sources to deliver seamless reporting to end users.</p>\r\n\r\nWe’ve worked hard for our reputation as a trusted and knowledgeable technology service provider. Through a combination of experience, client focus, and innovative technology, UBTI can become your trusted partner in delivering end-to-end solutions or in supplementing your internal resources on a project-by-project basis.\r\n\r\n<p>Contact us today to <a href="#" style="text-decoration: underline;" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#myModal">learn more.</a></p>', 'Finance', 'UBTI draws on its deep experience within the financial services industry to help institutions find innovative ways to optimize processes, reduce back office costs, manage risk, build customer loyalty, and navigate evolving competitive and regulatory landscapes. We offer end-to-end services and solutions that will give you the edge you need to make more informed decisions.', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'financial-services', '', '', '2017-01-05 09:29:05', '2017-01-05 09:29:05', '', 62, 'http://ubti/financial-services/', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(68, 1, '2015-07-27 01:38:32', '2015-07-27 01:38:32', '\r\n<div class="strip"> health plans <img src="http://ubti.brmdevsite.com/content/uploads/2016/10/dot11.png" />  providers <img src="http://ubti.brmdevsite.com/content/uploads/2016/10/dot11.png" /> hospitals </div>\r\n<img class="img-responsive" src="http://ubti.brmdevsite.com/content/uploads/2016/11/img_hel.png" width="100%" />\r\nToday’s healthcare environment is more complex than ever before. Health plans, medical groups, and providers alike are discovering that custom software is necessary to meet fundamental business and operational needs. When it comes to affordable, customized health IT solutions, UBTI’s Healthcare Professional Services team is an industry-recognized resource, offering domain expertise, quick-start healthcare modules, and data interface. UBTI provides economical and efficient technology solutions built for your increasingly complex environment.\r\n\r\n<strong>UBTI’s Expertise</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Significant experience with Community-Based Electronic Health Record (EHR) to automatically populate and share patient historical data and information throughout the Care chain, Referrals, Claims and Encounter transactions related to Health Plans, Rule engines that process the claims, and referrals, rule engines that creates user specific alerts based on their clinical data, Face Sheet which is a one stop solution to know the complete member Information, HCC score that helps the plans to identify physician’s efficiency in care management and the clinical decision support tools to manage the quality and cost of patient care.</li>\r\n	<li>Significant experience in dealing with MSOs, ACOs, IPAs, medical groups, health plan organizations, healthcare providers and payers.</li>\r\n	<li>Significant experience in Healthcare dashboards related to quality of care, disease management, case Management and clinical Analysis</li>\r\n	<li> Significant experience in dealing with electronic transactions and interfaces including Cigna, HealthNet, Blue Shield, PacifiCare, Aetna, Molina etc.</li>\r\n	<li> Significant experience in dealing with various platforms and systems including IDX, EZ-CAP, Milliman etc.</li>\r\n	<li>Supports a variety of different interface formats including NSF, XML, Flat file, Print Images, CAQH Core EDI 837 &amp; 237</li>\r\n	<li>Significant experience with regulatory compliances such as ICD10, Meaningful use, HIPPA and more, using a variety of tools.</li>\r\n	<li>Significant expertise in creation and automation of workflows to ensure compliance with federal, state and industry requirements.</li>\r\n	<li>Re-engineering and Implementation of Pre-Admission Screening and Resident (PASRR) Review program, a federally mandated program using UBTI\'S accelerator Trinity.</li>\r\n	<li>Experienced in developing customized reports for third-party product solutions like Trizetto.</li>\r\n	<li>Expertise in development and implementation of end-to-end health insurance claim management system.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>How can we help?</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>UBTI\'s Healthcare Professional Services team offers a depth of experience in all facets of current and legacy systems, delivering consulting and IT technology solutions to help integrated delivery systems and physician groups with data extraction, real-time data integration, and data exchange optimization.</li>\r\n	<li>Converting the existing legacy system to new technology-based web system to suit the modernized business environment in a modular way, with embedded business rules and workflow.</li>\r\n	<li>​Development of customized reports to suit your business needs.</li>\r\n	<li>End-to-end Application and Solution Development.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Contact us today to <a href="#" style="text-decoration: underline;" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#myModal">learn more.</a></p>  ', 'Healthcare', 'UBTI provides economical and efficient technology solutions built for your increasingly complex environment. Our experienced Healthcare Professional Services Practice provides consulting and software development services that enable MSOs, ACOs, IPAs, medical groups, health plan organizations, and healthcare providers to perform at the highest levels. We are able to rapidly customize and integrate reliable healthcare software modules, extend your current applications, and optimize native reporting capabilities to accelerate implementations and lower costs. This innovative, low-risk and yet efficient approach allows for flexibility and delivers significant cost savings.', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'healthcare', '', '', '2016-11-17 11:55:15', '2016-11-17 11:55:15', '', 62, 'http://ubti/healthcare/', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(70, 1, '2015-07-27 01:38:32', '2015-07-27 01:38:32', '<div class="row">\r\n<div class="col-md-6 col-sm-12 wow slideInLeft">\r\n\r\n<a href="#"><img class="img-responsive" src="https://placehold.it/600x250/CCCCCC/FFFFFF" alt="" /></a>\r\n<h2><a href="#">Development &amp; Maintenance</a></h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><a href="#">Gain a competitive advantage with high quality, feature-rich applications (Web, Mobile &amp; Cloud). developing applications that operate on-premises, in the cloud, and from mobiledevices is a core competency that UBTI can propel your business to the next level. We deliver the functionality your business needs while driving measurable improvements in quality, reliability and productivity.UBTI has designed a robust framework that serves as the infrastructure or foundation for many of our custom applications</a></p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-md-6 col-sm-12 wow slideInRight">\r\n\r\n<a href="#"><img class="img-responsive" src="https://placehold.it/600x250/CCCCCC/FFFFFF" alt="" /></a>\r\n<h2><a href="#">Data Integration &amp; Migration</a></h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><a href="#">Availability of data in different systems , sources , formats leads to challenges in decision making. We at UBTI are well experienced in aggregating and integrating data from different external sources into a centralized data repository which can provide full visibility and decision support across different domains. We can also help you with migration planning through execution so you can take advantage of converting the existing data into a new solution or changing the operating platforms.</a></p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="row">\r\n<div class="col-md-6 col-sm-12 wow slideInLeft">\r\n\r\n<a href="#"><img class="img-responsive" src="https://placehold.it/600x250/CCCCCC/FFFFFF" alt="" /></a>\r\n<h2><a href="#">Analytics &amp; Reporting</a></h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><a href="#">Managers and executives need the right information at the right time to make decisions.UBTI understands the value of having immediate access to highly relevant information and develops detailed analytics dashboards that display mission-critical data in an intuitive visual format. With the insight needed to take action, your organization can experience a new kind of collaboration that helps improve overall performance.</a></p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-md-6 col-sm-12 wow slideInRight">\r\n\r\n<a href="#"><img class="img-responsive" src="https://placehold.it/600x250/CCCCCC/FFFFFF" alt="" /></a>\r\n<h2><a href="#">Quality Assurance &amp; Testing</a></h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><a href="#">UBTI’s Quality Assurance activities aim to provide value to the customer. The testing processes followed at UBTI are mature, industry-standard, and proven to work. With our experienced QA personnel across various domains and technologies, we achieve high-quality deliverables through an independent, cost effective, on-time delivery, and zero-defective testing services. Our test repositories across all domains serve as a base, hence making the UBTI testing service an effective and reliable solution to the clients.</a></p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="row">\r\n<div class="col-md-6 col-md-offset-3 col-sm-12 wow slideInLeft">\r\n\r\n<a href="#"><img class="img-responsive" src="https://placehold.it/600x250/CCCCCC/FFFFFF" alt="" /></a>\r\n<h2><a href="#">Operation support &amp; Monitoring</a></h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><a href="#">Data refreshments need to happen at non-working hours. Realizing the effective monitoring needed for the data refreshment / integration, UBTI extends the support in monitoring the data refreshments and addressing the issues in a timely manner at a low cost. Clients get peace of mind knowing that their operation is under the watchful eye and care of UBTI support engineers during their non-working hours. Thus providing better customer satisfaction.</a></p>\r\n\r\n</di