(72, 1, '2015-07-27 01:38:32', '2015-07-27 01:38:32', '<strong>Development &amp; Maintenance for Competitive Advantage</strong>\r\n\r\nWe offer end-to-end product lifecycle services that extend across the technology stack, minimize development time and support multiple variants of your software without compromising quality. We combine deep industry experience, highly skilled resources, best-of-breed technologies, and proven processes to deliver software solutions that fully support your goals, mitigate risk, and maximize returns on your application investments. Our agile methodology leverages your existing development processes collaboratively while you capitalize on our compressed time-to-value iterative approach.\r\n\r\nSmoothly running, error-free, reliable, and high-value insight-generating applications are the hallmark of UBTI development and maintenance services.\r\n\r\n<strong>UBTI Capabilities</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Product definition</li>\r\n	<li>Design &amp; development</li>\r\n	<li>Validation, verification &amp; testing</li>\r\n	<li>Migration, re-engineering</li>\r\n	<li>Maintenance</li>\r\n	<li>Configuration management</li>\r\n	<li>Product enhancement – R&amp;D on adding new functionality to the product</li>\r\n	<li>Customization of the product</li>\r\n	<li>Implementation</li>\r\n	<li>Multiple interface support</li>\r\n	<li>Product implementation across geography</li>\r\n	<li>Product integration</li>\r\n	<li>Partnering with other third parties</li>\r\n	<li>User training</li>\r\n	<li>SaaS, virtualization and cloud</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>The UBTI Difference</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Deep technology expertise</li>\r\n	<li>Robust, scalable, and extensible application development and maintenance frameworks</li>\r\n	<li>Web-based delivery platform</li>\r\n	<li>End-to-end solution design and deployment</li>\r\n	<li>Innovative solutions that enrich legacy applications with the latest technologies</li>\r\n	<li>Highly experienced staff providing services in all aspects of application support and maintenance</li>\r\n	<li>On-call support to address high priority issues</li>\r\n	<li>Expertise in application optimization</li>\r\n	<li>Ability to adroitly migrate applications to align with changing business priorities</li>\r\n	<li>Intuitive sense of client application and maintenance needs</li>\r\n	<li>Knowledge sharing to guide client’s application acquisition strategies</li>\r\n	<li>Strategic global view regarding the importance of results-driven application management</li>\r\n	<li>A distinction marked by numerous highly-esteemed industry awards</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Contact us today to <a href="#" style="text-decoration: underline;" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#myModal">learn more.</a></p>', 'Development & Maintenance', 'Gain a competitive advantage with high quality, feature-rich applications (web, mobile, and cloud). Developing applications that operate on-premise, in the cloud, and from mobile devices is a core competency that will propel your business to the next level. We deliver functionality matched to your business needs and featuring the measurable improvements in quality, reliability, productivity, and business intelligence that are the hallmarks of UBTI.', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'development-and-maintenance', '', '', '2016-11-07 09:00:35', '2016-11-07 09:00:35', '', 70, 'http://ubti/development-and-maintenance/', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(74, 1, '2015-07-27 01:38:32', '2015-07-27 01:38:32', '<strong>Data Integration &amp; Migration for Greater Organizational Effectiveness</strong>\r\n\r\nBusinesses and government agencies operate in an increasingly dynamic and complex environment, relying on a variety of applications and source files that hold critical information about products, services, customers, suppliers, employees, and partners. Unfortunately, these systems often hold inconsistent, fragmented, and duplicate information. Unless the data is properly integrated and made accessible, making informed strategic and operational decisions will be difficult.\r\n\r\n<strong>Data Integration and Migration Experts</strong>\r\n\r\nUBTI’s proven methodologies streamline data integration efforts so you can remain agile and proactively responsive to an environment in continuous flux. Data integration is the aggregation of data from disparate sources and stored in a data warehouse or central database. A high-performance data integration solution will efficiently refresh the central database so you can query and gather valuable and actionable information on demand.\r\n\r\nUBTI can create an integrated infrastructure that provides the right data at the right time with services that include Extract, Transform and Load (ETL), Enterprise Information Integration (EII), Data Quality Assurance (DQA), and data management services, including Enterprise Application Integration (EAI).\r\n\r\nUBTI partners with clients to fully understand both their business and IT strategy. Then we provide a comprehensive solution that includes reliable, efficient, and easy-to-maintain processes to serve both your short and long-term objectives. We have at our fingertips the most advanced integration and migration tools and methodologies available for your benefit. We apply best industry data migration practices for data discovery, cleansing, monitoring, transforming, and delivery. We resolve inconsistencies among divergent source files with universally accepted business rules governing ETL processes.\r\n\r\nUBTI expertly performs data integration and migration services on-demand across multiple sources and targets, satisfying complex requirements with the best scalable runtimes available inside a secure environment. By embedding specialized integration and migration components in the base architecture we will optimize your data integration infrastructure so it can be more scalable, flawlessly process higher data volumes, and better leverage system resources for higher return on investment.\r\n\r\n<p>Contact us today to <a href="#" style="text-decoration: underline;" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#myModal">learn more.</a></p>', 'Data Integration & Migration', 'Availability of data in different systems, sources, and formats leads to challenges in decision making. We at UBTI, are highly experienced in aggregating and integrating data from different external sources into a centralized data repository that can provide full visibility and decision support across different domains.', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'data-integration-and-migration', '', '', '2016-11-07 09:01:32', '2016-11-07 09:01:32', '', 70, 'http://ubti/data-integration-and-migration/', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(76, 1, '2015-07-27 01:38:32', '2015-07-27 01:38:32', '<strong>Laser Focused Analytics</strong><strong> from </strong><strong>Detailed Reports and Dashboards</strong>\r\n\r\nManagers and executives need the right information at the right time to make the right decisions. But this can be challenging when the needed information lives in an ever-increasing array of disconnected systems, databases, and applications.\r\n\r\nUBTI’s business intelligence experts — specialists in aerospace, financial services and healthcare — understand the value of having immediate access to highly relevant information. We develop detailed highly visual, highly intuitive analytics dashboards that enable you to gain a better understanding of your business so you can address complex business challenges with confidence.\r\n\r\nOur dashboards are built with the end user in mind. Action items, threshold reporting services, and simple high level charts are key elements in providing you with a simple, real time look at what is most relevant to you. Each automated component gives the ability to drill down to see the details that are automatically aggregated and pushed to your individual dashboard.\r\n\r\n<strong>Custom Tailored Reporting</strong>\r\n\r\nUBTI also has experience in providing custom reporting.  From custom ad-hoc reports to trending reports and from advanced charts and graphs to mapping tools, we have the end-to-end experience in making valuable use of the data in your systems.\r\n\r\nUBTI has the deep knowledge and expertise with SQL Server Reporting Services (SSRS) needed to design advanced reporting systems that integrate disparate data sources and empower your users to make effective, informed decisions. Based on trusted data delivered in the appropriate format, these services complement existing reporting workflows, taking them to the next level with advanced scheduling and ad-hoc reporting capabilities. Reporting services can also be easily integrated with content management systems such as Microsoft SharePoint so you can create, modify, and publish reports from within SharePoint.\r\n\r\n<strong>We can help with:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Drill-down/drill-through to details</li>\r\n 	<li>Dashboard personalization</li>\r\n 	<li>Role-based views and access</li>\r\n 	<li>Configurable alerts</li>\r\n 	<li>Financial reporting views</li>\r\n 	<li>Milestone performance views</li>\r\n 	<li>Top 5 lists</li>\r\n 	<li>Reliable and timely reporting</li>\r\n 	<li>Single-delivery platform for reports across systems</li>\r\n 	<li>Independent web-based delivery mechanism using active directory</li>\r\n 	<li>Automatic delivery to mailbox</li>\r\n 	<li>Prebuilt customizable ad-hoc framework</li>\r\n 	<li>Integration with content management systems (CMS)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Contact us today to <a href="#" style="text-decoration: underline;" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#myModal">learn more.</a></p>', 'Analytics & Reporting', 'Managers and executives need the right information at the right time to make decisions. But this can be challenging when the information lives in an ever-increasing array of disconnected systems, databases, and applications. UBTI understands the value of having immediate access to highly relevant information and develops detailed analytics dashboards that display mission-critical data in an intuitive visual format.', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'analytics-and-reporting', '', '', '2016-11-07 09:01:12', '2016-11-07 09:01:12', '', 70, 'http://ubti/analytics-and-reporting/', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(78, 1, '2015-07-27 01:38:32', '2015-07-27 01:38:32', '<strong>Domain-Focused Quality Assurance</strong>\r\n\r\nUBTI’s quality assurance aims to provide solutions that exceed our clients’ highest standards in key domains that include health insurance, healthcare, education, and finance (asset management).\r\n\r\nOur experienced quality team leverages domain-specific expertise across multiple technologies to consistently assure all our deliverables exceed the most stringent quality standards through independent, cost-effective, on-time, and zero-defect testing services.\r\n\r\nThose services rely on a solid quality framework of best industry practices characterized by effective strategy, defined processes, proper execution, comprehensive scope, and end-to-end test engineering solutions.\r\n\r\nOur test offerings are divided into three main categories: basic, specialized, and Test Factory.\r\n\r\n<strong>Basic Offerings</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>System Testing</li>\r\n	<li>System Integration Testing</li>\r\n	<li>User Acceptance Testing</li>\r\n	<li>Interface Testing</li>\r\n	<li>Regression Testing</li>\r\n	<li>Accessibility Testing</li>\r\n	<li>Load, Volume &amp; Stress Testing</li>\r\n	<li>Automated Testing (Selenium)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Specialized Offerings</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Packaged Application Testing</li>\r\n	<li>Product Testing</li>\r\n	<li>Web Testing</li>\r\n	<li>ETL Testing</li>\r\n	<li>Mobile Testing</li>\r\n	<li>Big Data Testing</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Test Factory</strong>\r\n\r\nA readymade repository of tests in various domains that can be used or referenced in order to accelerate test case development and test execution\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Health Insurance</li>\r\n	<li>Healthcare</li>\r\n	<li>Finance (Asset management)</li>\r\n	<li>Education</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Contact us today to <a href="#" style="text-decoration: underline;" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#myModal">learn more.</a></p>', 'QA & Testing', 'UBTI’s quality assurance activities enable extreme client value from our experienced QA teams across multiple domains and technologies. We achieve high-quality deliverables through our independent, cost effective, on-time, and zero-defect testing. Our test repositories across all domains provide the foundation on which UBTI testing services become an effective and reliable solution to clients.', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'qa-and-testing', '', '', '2016-11-07 09:01:02', '2016-11-07 09:01:02', '', 70, 'http://ubti/qa-and-testing/', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(80, 1, '2015-07-27 01:38:33', '2015-07-27 01:38:33', '<strong>Trusted, Affordable 24/7 Operations Support &amp; Monitoring</strong>\r\n\r\nWhen your IT operations go offline, so does your business — losing customers, frustrating employees, and disrupting the delivery of products and services. Today’s systems are complex, highly interdependent, and mission critical — requiring highly specialized skills to always be ready whenever issues occur that could potentially impact your business. But having senior-level experts on staff and always available is expensive. So organizations need a partner they can trust to ensure IT operations always stay at peak performance while support costs stay in check.\r\n\r\n<strong>Skilled IT Experts, Always Ready</strong>\r\n\r\nUBTI has the skilled experts and technical resources to deliver the 24/7 IT operation monitoring service today’s “always on” organizations require. We take a proactive approach to continuous monitoring, which includes monitoring the appropriate service level benchmarks and response protocols in the event threatening conditions or a system failure occurs. That includes an alert elevation protocol that rallies qualified resources to immediately resolve issues. UBTI’s experienced staff provides meticulous oversight, impeccable decision-making, and sound judgment that aligns with your policies and procedures. UBTI’s watchful management also provides early warning of potential service problems so they can be resolved before customers or employees become aware of them.\r\n\r\nLook to UBTI to achieve far more reliable IT operations without the need to rely on in-house technical resource during non-working hours. Our round-the-clock support experts are highly experienced at monitoring vendor data feeds, SLA parameters, and job execution status updates — and will resolve any problems through effective and efficient interactions and follow-ups with appropriate internal and external resources.\r\n\r\n<p>Contact us today to <a href="#" style="text-decoration: underline;" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#myModal">learn more.</a></p>', 'Operation Support & Monitoring', 'Data refresh needs to happen during non-working hours. Understanding the monitoring requirements for effective data refresh / integration, UBTI offers extended support to monitor data refresh and addresses any issues in a timely manner at affordable cost. Clients get peace of mind knowing that their operation is under the watchful eye and care of UBTI support engineers during clients’ non-working hours.', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'operation-support-and-monitoring', '', '', '2016-11-07 09:00:51', '2016-11-07 09:00:51', '', 70, 'http://ubti/operation-support-and-monitoring/', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(82, 1, '2015-07-27 01:38:33', '2015-07-27 01:38:33', '<div class="row">\r\n<div class="col-md-4 col-sm-12"><a href="#"><img class="img-responsive wow slideInLeft" src="https://placehold.it/500x250/CCCCCC/FFFFFF" alt="" /></a></div>\r\n<div class="col-md-8 col-sm-12 wow slideInRight">\r\n<h2><a href="#">Capstone</a></h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><a href="#">Capstone is UBTI’s signature suite of innovative tools designed to manage the performance of your Programs, Suppliers, and Quality Management System. Capstone provides your organization with full visibility into performance and execution, regulatory compliance, customer satisfaction, and quality control.</a></p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="row">\r\n<div class="col-md-4 col-sm-12"><a href="#"><img class="img-responsive wow slideInLeft" src="https://placehold.it/500x250/CCCCCC/FFFFFF" alt="" /></a></div>\r\n<div class="col-md-8 col-sm-12 wow slideInRight">\r\n<h2><a href="#">Trinity Framework</a></h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><a href="#">Trinity Frameworks are our easy-to-use reusable component library that is developed on the asp.net MVC framework. The library comes with many reusable components that incorporate the latest development patterns and practices to simplify development time.</a></p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="row">\r\n<div class="col-md-4 col-sm-12"><a href="#"><img class="img-responsive wow slideInLeft" src="https://placehold.it/500x250/CCCCCC/FFFFFF" alt="" /></a></div>\r\n<div class="col-md-8 col-sm-12 wow slideInRight">\r\n<h2><a href="#">Financial Reporting System</a></h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><a href="#">UBTI offers state-of-the-art technology to easily query financial data and generate key performance indicators, reports, and analytics. We have developed a sophisticated financial reporting system to give you the most trusted information available,also tools to effectively and confidently advise your clients in attaining their financial objectives.</a></p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Solutions', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'solutions', '', '', '2016-02-26 06:49:22', '2016-02-26 06:49:22', '', 0, 'http://ubti/solutions/', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(84, 1, '2015-07-27 01:38:33', '2015-07-27 01:38:33', '<p style="text-align: left;"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-216 size-medium" src="http://ubti.brmdevsite.com/content/uploads/2015/07/capstone-suite-300x122.png" alt="capstone-suite" width="300" height="122" /></p>\r\n<strong>Capstone Performance Visibility Suite™</strong>\r\n\r\nCapstone is UBTI’s signature suite of innovative tools designed to manage the performance of procurement programs, suppliers, and quality management systems. Capstone provides your organization with full visibility into performance and execution, regulatory compliance, customer satisfaction, and quality control. This fully integrated suite is comprised of four modules:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Program Performance</li>\r\n 	<li>Supplier Performance</li>\r\n 	<li>Quality Management</li>\r\n 	<li>Alert Management</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nThese modules operate in concert to give you the visibility needed to ensure that your organization’s procurement programs, suppliers, quality management system, and processes are meeting your expectations and your customers’.\r\n\r\n<strong>What is Capstone?</strong>\r\n\r\nDeveloped by industry innovators at UBTI, Capstone Performance Visibility Suite™ is an innovative suite of software modules for managing procurement program performance, suppliers, quality, and product reliability alerts.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class="aligncenter wp-image-217" src="http://ubti.brmdevsite.com/content/uploads/2015/07/capstone-org-300x226.png" alt="capstone-org" width="390" height="294" />\r\n\r\nCapstone was designed and developed by IT and program management professionals with a deep experience in the information technology, aerospace, defense and healthcare industries. It was designed for ease of use and to provide fingertip access to key information dashboards showing the state of health of your enterprise and programs, as well as the status of actions.\r\n\r\nEach module comes with its own highly intuitive user interface, providing you with a status update, by glancing at key performance indicators and actions. Capstone can generate status reports on the fly with just the click of a mouse. It is designed to operate either in concert with your existing ERP system or as a standalone system. Capstone can be installed on your server to operate behind your firewall or on a secure cloud that we provide to you. Capstone can also be customized to give you additional functionality to support your unique needs.\r\n\r\n<strong>Capstone Program Performance</strong>\r\n\r\nThe Capstone Program Performance module provides program managers and management with high-level visibility into key elements of program performance and execution including:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Technical</li>\r\n 	<li>Cost</li>\r\n 	<li>Schedule</li>\r\n 	<li>Quality</li>\r\n 	<li>Supplier</li>\r\n 	<li>Risk</li>\r\n 	<li>Customer Satisfaction</li>\r\n 	<li>Product Reliability and Recalls</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<a href="http://ubti.brmdevsite.com/solutions/capstone/capstone-program-performance/"><b><u>Learn More</u></b></a>\r\n\r\n<strong>Capstone Supplier Performance</strong>\r\n\r\nThe Capstone Supplier Performance Module provides full insight into the performance of your supply chain including:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Ability to assess all types of supplier work, including design and development, operations and maintenance, hardware and software production and lower-tier supplier management</li>\r\n 	<li>Selectable assessment templates, categories, frequencies and approval workflows</li>\r\n 	<li>Email notification for assessment writers and approvers</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<a href="http://ubti.brmdevsite.com/solutions/capstone/capstone-supplier-performance/"><b><u>Learn More</u></b></a>\r\n\r\n<strong>Capstone Quality Management</strong>\r\n\r\nThe Capstone Quality Management Module manages key elements of your Quality Management System including:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Supplier Certifications</li>\r\n 	<li>Internal and Supplier Audits</li>\r\n 	<li>Corrective and Preventive Actions</li>\r\n 	<li>Supplier Qualifications and Scope of Approval</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<a href="http://ubti.brmdevsite.com/solutions/capstone/capstone-quality-mangement/"><b><u>Learn More</u></b></a>\r\n\r\n<strong>Capstone Alert Management</strong>\r\n\r\nThe Capstone Alert Management Module provides closed-loop notification and reporting of priority actions such as the Government Industry Data Exchange Program (GIDEP) alerts for reliability and counterfeit parts issues. Some of the key features include:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Compatibility with the new Counterfeit Parts Prevention Standard AS5553</li>\r\n 	<li>Rapid alert disseminations</li>\r\n 	<li>Closed-loop reporting of usage and impact assessments</li>\r\n 	<li>Highly-accessible records of alert notifications and actions</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<a href="http://ubti.brmdevsite.com/solutions/capstone/capstone-alert-management/"><b><u>Learn More</u></b></a>\r\n\r\n<strong>Capstone Performance Visibility Suite Highlights </strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Information dashboards to monitor and manage a portfolio of programs</li>\r\n 	<li>Real-time visibility into key program performance elements, including technical, cost, schedule, quality, supplier, risk, customer Satisfaction, product reliability, and recalls</li>\r\n 	<li>Customer satisfaction tools to assess, monitor, and manage your customers’ experience</li>\r\n 	<li>A robust database enables search of all current and previous product reliability and counterfeit parts alerts</li>\r\n 	<li>Report generation features capture and convert key data into complete reports using standardized dashboards</li>\r\n 	<li>Ability to track supplier performance down to your supplier’s business unit and project</li>\r\n 	<li>Scalable tools that dynamically fit your organization</li>\r\n 	<li>Integration with your existing ERP systems</li>\r\n 	<li>Standardized reporting across your enterprise</li>\r\n 	<li>Workflow, template, and role creation based on customizable organizational structures</li>\r\n 	<li>Secure authentication and authorization</li>\r\n 	<li>Audit trails that can be used for CMMI, AS9100, AS5553 and more</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Contact us today to <a href="#" style="text-decoration: underline;" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#myModal">learn more.</a></p>', 'Capstone', 'Capstone is UBTI’s signature suite of innovative tools designed to manage the performance of an organization’s programs, suppliers and quality management system. Capstone provide  full visibility into performance and execution, regulatory compliance, customer satisfaction, and quality control.', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'capstone', '', '', '2016-11-07 08:58:01', '2016-11-07 08:58:01', '', 82, 'http://ubti/capstone/', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(86, 1, '2015-07-27 01:38:33', '2015-07-27 01:38:33', '<strong>Innovate with Proven High-Tech Solutions</strong>\r\n\r\nWe have an internal R&amp;D team dedicated to developing proprietary model frameworks and code that we can readily use in the field. To date, we have amassed a diverse and comprehensive library of modular frameworks and functionally efficient code. This proprietary intellectual property provides us with a wealth of proven approaches to consider when formulating technology solutions. We can afford the luxury of innovating with known inputs that are pre-tested and low-risk. Our proprietary frameworks and code give us the advantages of speed and low cost that we can pass on to you.\r\n\r\n<strong>Readily Available Frameworks</strong>\r\n\r\nOur research and development team has developed reusable technology frameworks that allow us to rapidly develop any custom application on a tested and debugged framework. The Trinity Framework is cloud-ready and employs an SOA (services oriented architecture) so developers can easily plug and play its services into other applications — freeing them to focus on creating distinctive value-adding functionality, not reinventing the wheel.\r\n\r\n<strong>Available Components</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>User Maintenance</li>\r\n	<li>Role Maintenance</li>\r\n	<li>Menu Maintenance</li>\r\n	<li>Organization Hierarchy</li>\r\n	<li>Authentication</li>\r\n	<li>Authorization – Privilege Based, Role Based</li>\r\n	<li>Custom Menus Based on Roles</li>\r\n	<li>Grid Component with Paging, Sorting and Filtering</li>\r\n	<li>HTML Helpers for easy rendering widely used control</li>\r\n	<li>PDF Engine using iTextsharp (free edition)/ EssentialPDF</li>\r\n	<li>Mobile Support – Device Specific View Engine</li>\r\n	<li>Multi-Tenant (can be used as single tenant too)</li>\r\n	<li>Organizational hierarchy with archiving capability to keep historical structure intact</li>\r\n	<li>Dashboard Widgets</li>\r\n	<li>Generic HTML Helpers</li>\r\n	<li>Email Support</li>\r\n	<li>Application Log</li>\r\n	<li>Error Log</li>\r\n	<li>Other Plugins\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>jQuery-UI based plugins for tabs, calendar, autocomplete</li>\r\n	<li>CSS driven, Easy to change the look and feel</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>We help you to</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Leverage tested and debugged frameworks and programming code</li>\r\n	<li>Speed development time</li>\r\n	<li>Reduce time spent on administrative functions through reusable component library which can be integrated</li>\r\n	<li>Save on development costs</li>\r\n	<li>Stand up applications quickly</li>\r\n	<li>Reduce overhead by incurring amortization costs instead of fully-loaded labor costs</li>\r\n	<li>Have the option to acquire future framework upgrades</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;', 'Trinity Framework', 'Trinity Frameworks is our easy-to-use reusable component library that is developed on the asp.net MVC framework. The library comes with many reusable components that incorporate the latest development patterns and practices in order to simplify development and shorten development time.', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'trinity-framework', '', '', '2016-04-11 12:44:25', '2016-04-11 12:44:25', '', 82, 'http://ubti/trinity-framework/', 0, 'page', '', 0) ;
