(88, 1, '2015-07-27 01:38:33', '2015-07-27 01:38:33', '<img class="img-responsive" style="padding:6px 0 0 0;" src="http://ubti.brmdevsite.com/content/uploads/2016/12/img2_fras.png" width="100%" />\r\n\r\nSpreadsheet-based reporting is time-consuming and makes sharing information a hassle. It can be challenging for technology teams without a streamlined reporting system to keep up with requests for valuation, risk, and analytics reports.  \r\n\r\nFortunately, there’s a proven solution to speed things up. UBTI’s Financial Reporting & Analytics Solution (FRAS) seamlessly integrates internal and external applications to provide an analytical view for executive dashboards, reports, and drill down details.\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Enhanced Portfolio Visibility</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<h6 align="center" style="padding-bottom:0px; margin-bottom:0px"><img class="img-responsive" src="http://ubti.brmdevsite.com/content/uploads/2017/01/new_fras_gra.png" /></h6>\r\n<p align="center"  style="font-style:italic;color:#999999; font-family: \'Droid Serif\', serif;\r\n padding:0px 0 0 0;">The dashboard shows essential data from multiple applications, all in one place.</p>\r\n\r\nThe FRAS solution is easy to use. UBTI sets it up by integrating separate systems such as CRM, trading, and accounting, to name a few. The firm’s users are then assigned specific levels of access rights depending on their role. The users can now view essential data from numerous systems all in one place, bringing efficiency and clarity to the decision-making process.\r\n\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Generate Reports with Just a Few Clicks</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<img class="img-responsive" src="http://ubti.brmdevsite.com/content/uploads/2017/01/perfor_com_report_last.png" style="padding:0px 0 0 0;" /></p>\r\n\r\nUsers can quickly display graphs and run reports on critical information such as:\r\n\r\n<div class="ind_other">\r\n<div class="col-md-5">\r\n<ul>\r\n\r\n<li style="list-style:none;"><strong><img src="http://ubti.brmdevsite.com/content/uploads/2016/10/tick.png" /></strong> Asset allocation</li>\r\n<li style="list-style:none;"><strong><img src="http://ubti.brmdevsite.com/content/uploads/2016/10/tick.png" /></strong> Sector analysis by industry</li>\r\n<li style="list-style:none;"><strong><img src="http://ubti.brmdevsite.com/content/uploads/2016/10/tick.png" /></strong> Portfolio analysis</li>\r\n<li style="list-style:none;"><strong><img src="http://ubti.brmdevsite.com/content/uploads/2016/10/tick.png" /></strong> Transaction / commission report</li>\r\n<li style="list-style:none;"><strong><img src="http://ubti.brmdevsite.com/content/uploads/2016/10/tick.png" /></strong> Performance history</li>	\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="col-md-6">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li style="list-style:none;"><strong><img src="http://ubti.brmdevsite.com/content/uploads/2016/10/tick.png" /></strong> Portfolio summary, by asset class or</li>\r\n<li style="list-style:none; padding:0 0 0 18px;">security type</li>\r\n<li style="list-style:none;"><strong><img src="http://ubti.brmdevsite.com/content/uploads/2016/10/tick.png" /></strong> Holdings by sector, industry, </li>\r\n<li style="list-style:none;"><strong><img src="http://ubti.brmdevsite.com/content/uploads/2016/10/tick.png" /></strong> Exposure by country, currency</li>\r\n<li style="list-style:none;"><strong><img src="http://ubti.brmdevsite.com/content/uploads/2016/10/tick.png" /></strong> Reference data listings</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="clear:both;"></div>\r\n<p></p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p style="padding:0 0 20px 0;">Ready to enjoy the convenience of a streamlined reporting system?</p>\r\n\r\n<h6 align="center" style="padding-bottom:0px; margin-bottom:0px"><a href="#" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#myModal"><img src="http://ubti.brmdevsite.com/content/uploads/2016/12/button_1.png" /></a></h6>\r\n<p align="center"  style="font-style:italic; padding:0px 0 0 0;">Reduce turnaround time and lower costs.</p>', 'Financial Reporting & Analytics Solution', 'UBTI offers state-of-the-art technology to easily query financial data and generate key performance indicators, reports, and analytics. We have developed a sophisticated financial reporting system to give you the most trusted information available along with the tools to effectively and confidently advise your clients on how to reach their financial objectives.', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'financial-reporting-and-analytics-solution', '', '', '2017-01-24 11:38:17', '2017-01-24 11:38:17', '', 82, 'http://ubti/financial-reporting-system/', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(101, 1, '2015-07-27 02:03:39', '2015-07-27 02:03:39', '<img class="wp-image-940 alignright" src="http://ubti.brmdevsite.com/content/uploads/2015/07/mission-image.jpg" alt="mission-image" width="395" height="373" /></Br><strong>Mission</strong>\r\nTo empower and transform organizations and individuals through the consistent blending of innovative technology, business excellence,and the Biblical values of honesty, integrity, accountability, and serving one another.</Br></Br>\r\n<strong>Vision</strong>\r\nOur vision is to be a profitable, global and technology-based organization that serves thousands of employees, customers, and partners using principles of honesty, integrity, accountability, and serving one another as its guiding light and measure.\r\n\r\n<strong>Core Values</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Honesty, integrity, and highest level business ethics</li>\r\n 	<li>Fiercely competitive in the marketplace</li>\r\n 	<li>Market segment domination as the goal in each segment</li>\r\n 	<li>A fun place to work where people respect each other</li>\r\n 	<li>A place where everyone is a contributor and peak performer in their role</li>\r\n 	<li>Innovation, creative thinking and a "can do" attitude is part of the culture</li>\r\n 	<li>Unyielding focus on customer engagement and loyalty</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Mission, Vision & Core values', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'mission', '', '', '2016-11-17 13:32:40', '2016-11-17 13:32:40', '', 109, 'http://ubti/mission/', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(105, 1, '2015-07-27 02:03:39', '2015-07-27 02:03:39', '<strong>Qualifications</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Professionalism, Dedication and Integrity</strong>\r\n\r\nUBTI sets itself apart by providing cost-efficient and technically innovative solutions. We use our domain and industry expertise to develop custom solutions that connect information silos so that meaningful data can be extracted and made accessible to drive better decision making. Our world-class professionals pride themselves on earning customer loyalty by delivering the best possible service. We provide our clients with swift scheduling and rapid turnaround. Your business issues offer us challenges that we are well-qualified to handle, and which we address with enthusiasm and determination.\r\n\r\n<strong>Information Technology Consulting\r\n</strong>\r\nOur professional team of technology consultants bring a wide variety of knowledge and skills, combined with functional and industry experience, to serve the high-demanding consulting and strategic planning needs of our clients for customized software, database design and development solutions. We have the flexibility to accomodate the diversity of your special requirements with services from our pre-qualified, experienced information technology consultants on both short and long-term assignments. Those assignments can range from evaluation and needs assessment - to selecting appropriate technologies,  tools, and project management solution - to developing a complete end-to-end application or software product.\r\n\r\nWe are extensively experienced in designing enterprise-wide architecture and IT strategic plans for companies of all shapes and sizes -- from Fortune 500 companies to small and medium-sized businesses. Our world-class consultants rapidly assess and anticipate resource requirements, then quickly align and deploy our team of experts who then drive development to take advantage of windows of opportunities. We help you quickly access meaningful data, aggregate and organize the resulting business intelligence, develop predictive analytics, capitalize competitive advantages, make profitable business decisions, and stay attuned to changing business climates.\r\n\r\n<strong>Microsoft Partner</strong>\r\n\r\nAs a Microsoft Certified Partner, UBTI delivers the highest level technical expertise, strategic thinking and hands-on skills. We provide a broad range of experience, vendor affiliations and real-world perspective that help you prioritize and develop your technology needs. Our Microsoft Certified developers are knowledgeable, experienced and committed professionals who assess and address organizational needs, and deliver targeted solutions that surpass client expectations.\r\n\r\n<strong>Core Capabilities &amp; Expertise</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Application Development, Customization &amp; Maintenance (Windows/Web/Mobile/Cloud)</li>\r\n 	<li>Legacy Application Migration/Modernization</li>\r\n 	<li>Data Integration/Migration</li>\r\n 	<li>Independent Validation and Verifications</li>\r\n 	<li>Business Intelligence, Analytics and Reporting</li>\r\n 	<li>Operation Support and Monitoring</li>\r\n 	<li>Application Migration/Re-Engineering</li>\r\n 	<li>Database / Tools Upgradation Support</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Representative Examples of Completed Work</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Aerospace\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Supplier/ Program/ Quality Management Systems</li>\r\n 	<li>Executing Reporting Systems</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li>Financial Services\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Data Management/ Integration/ Migration/ Reporting/ Portal Application Development/ Customization/ Maintenance for Multiple Asset Management Companies (Financial Services)</li>\r\n 	<li>Independent Validation and Verification of Trade Order Management System and Client Reporting System</li>\r\n 	<li>Database and ETL Tool Migrations/ Re-Engineering</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li>Healthcare\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>End-to-End Healthcare product / Solution</li>\r\n 	<li>Health Insurance Product/ Solution</li>\r\n 	<li>Pre-admission Screening and Resident Review (PASRR) System</li>\r\n 	<li>Provider Dispute System</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li>Others\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>School Computerization and Management System</li>\r\n 	<li>Quiz Management Application System (Mobile)</li>\r\n 	<li>Digital Library Management System (Mobile/ Big-Data)</li>\r\n 	<li>Work Permit Management System</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Technology Expertise</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Microsoft Products (Win Forms/ ASP.NET/ ASP.NET MVC/ C#.NET/ VB.NET/ WPF/ WCF)</li>\r\n 	<li>Microsoft SQL Server 2008, 2008 R2, 2012 and 2014</li>\r\n 	<li>Business Intelligence (SSRS / SSIS / SSAS/ Power BI/ Data Mining)</li>\r\n 	<li>Cloud Services</li>\r\n 	<li>Biz Talk</li>\r\n 	<li>Controls (Telerik/ Dev Express)</li>\r\n 	<li>Design Technologies (HTML 5/ CSS3/ Ace Theme Bootstrap)</li>\r\n 	<li>Jquery and Java scripts</li>\r\n 	<li>Mobile App Development\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>XCode (Mac) - For iOS development</li>\r\n 	<li>Apache Cordova (Phonegap)</li>\r\n 	<li>SQLite</li>\r\n 	<li>ApacheCouch DB</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Awards</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Our Commitment</strong>\r\n\r\nUBTI is committed to providing exceptional technology consulting services and solutions to our clients. We consistently strive to deliver cost-effective, high-performing, and innovative technology solutions. When we receive an award, it means we are doing our job and doing it right. Recognition by our clients is the source of our greatest satisfaction. Below are some of our most recent awards.\r\n\r\n<strong>2011 Supplier Excellence Award - Northrop Grumman Corporation</strong>\r\n\r\nNorthrop Grumman has recognized UBTI, Inc. for outstanding performance as one of its top suppliers. We received the Supplier Excellence Award during the annual ceremony at Northrop Grumman’s corporate headquarters in Falls Church, VA. The award recognized UBTI for scheduling integrity, project management, responsiveness, technical competence, financial oversight, and mission assurance.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://ubti.brmdevsite.com/content/uploads/2015/07/award.pdf" target="_blank">Northrop Grumman Press Release [PDF]</a>\r\n\r\n<strong>2008 and 2005 Supplier Excellence Award - Northrop Grumman Corporation</strong>\r\n\r\nNorthrop Grumman has twice honored UBTI with its coveted Supplier Excellence Award once in 2008 and 2005. UBTI was recognized for technical innovations, quality products and services and outstanding performance—all of which significantly benefited Northrop Grumman and its government and commercial customers.\r\n\r\n<strong>Chamber of Commerce Small Business of the Year</strong>\r\n\r\nUBTI was named the 2008 Small Business of the Year by the Anaheim California Chamber of Commerce. The award, given in partnership with the City of Anaheim and the Small Business Association, recognizes companies such as UBTI for exceptional business achievement and outstanding commitment to Anaheim’s business community.\r\n\r\n<a><img class="alignnone wp-image-157" src="http://ubti.brmdevsite.com/content/uploads/2015/07/awards.png" alt="awards" width="169" height="65" /></a>    <a><img class="alignnone wp-image-158" src="http://ubti.brmdevsite.com/content/uploads/2015/07/award2.png" alt="award2" width="188" height="54" /></a>   <a><img class="alignnone wp-image-159" src="http://ubti.brmdevsite.com/content/uploads/2015/07/award-3.png" alt="award 3" width="152" height="35" /></a> <a><img class="alignnone wp-image-160" src="http://ubti.brmdevsite.com/content/uploads/2015/07/award-4.png" alt="award 4" width="131" height="56" /></a>\r\n\r\n<p>Contact us today to <a href="#" style="text-decoration: underline;" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#myModal">learn more.</a></p>  ', 'Qualifications & Awards', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'qualifications-and-awards', '', '', '2016-11-17 13:28:56', '2016-11-17 13:28:56', '', 109, 'http://ubti/qualifications-and-awards/', 0, 'page', '', 0),
