(294, 1, '2015-08-06 09:44:14', '2015-08-06 09:44:14', '<strong>Tools &amp; Solutions for Procurement Program Managers</strong>\r\n\r\nThe growing burden on organizations to execute programs with flawless performance is driving the need for procurement program managers to stay on top of every critical detail. Capstone is an innovative and user-friendly solution that lets you monitor and manage the performance of your programs using heads-up displays and graphics of real-time critical data.\r\n\r\n<strong>Designed with Program Managers in Mind</strong>\r\n\r\nCapstone’s unique design places it at the center of a network that connects suppliers, customers, internal organizations, and programs. From informational dashboards that provide high-level visibility into critical performance measures to an on-demand feature that lets you generate reports in a manner of seconds, Capstone is taking procurement program performance to the next level. Customer satisfaction is key. Embedded within this module are additional tools for analyzing customer expectations and achieving greater customer satisfaction. Capstone Program Performance also features easy-to-complete templates that let you review your programs’ performance each month and get trend analysis to detect potential performance issues before they become real problems.\r\n\r\n<strong>Capstone Program Performance Highlights</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Real-time visibility into key program performance elements including technical, cost, schedule, quality, supplier, risk, customer satisfaction, and quality</li>\r\n	<li>Information dashboards that can be customized to monitor and manage individual project details as well as a complete portfolio of programs</li>\r\n	<li>Customer satisfaction tools to assess, monitor, and manage your customers’ expectations</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Contact us today to <a href="#" style="text-decoration: underline;" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#myModal">learn more.</a></p>', 'Capstone Program Performance', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'capstone-program-performance', '', '', '2016-11-07 08:56:43', '2016-11-07 08:56:43', '', 84, 'http://ubti.zetalight.com/?page_id=294', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(296, 1, '2015-08-06 09:53:42', '2015-08-06 09:53:42', 'Our Capstone Quality Management module monitors, assesses, and controls internal and external processes, resources, and material that comprise your quality management system. Capstone Quality Management enables your procurement program and quality managers to make key time-sensitive decisions using real-time data. Capstone also uses an embedded workflow for action item assignment, tracking, and approval.\r\n\r\n<strong>The Centerpiece of Your Quality Management System</strong>\r\n\r\nThe Capstone Quality Management module includes functionality for supplier certification control, audit management, and a corrective / preventative action system (CPAS). All of these functions are comprehensive, intuitive, easy to use, and easy to navigate.\r\n\r\n<strong>Audits Become Much Easier to Pass with Capstone</strong>\r\n\r\nCapstone contains many of the key elements of AS9100 and ISO 9001. You can show auditors objective evidence that you are in control of your processes, including control of your supply chain, scope of approval of your suppliers, and verification of corrective actions. Capstone contains all the evidence you need to pass your audits. Just point and click to the needed data to demonstrate compliance.\r\n\r\n<strong>Capstone Quality Management Highlights:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Seamless integration with existing programs, suppliers, ERP, and organizational structure</li>\r\n	<li>Easy access to data</li>\r\n	<li>Heads-up executive dashboard with “State of Health” metrics</li>\r\n	<li>Adherence to industry best practices for Corrective Actions (AS9100 8.5.2), Preventative Actions (AS9100 8.5.3) and Supplier Scope of Approval (AS9100 7.4.1.a)</li>\r\n	<li>Connected to the Alert Management, Program Performance, and Supplier Performance modules</li>\r\n	<li>Full reporting capability</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Contact us today to <a href="#" style="text-decoration: underline;" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#myModal">learn more.</a></p>', 'Capstone Quality Mangement', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'capstone-quality-mangement', '', '', '2016-11-07 08:57:05', '2016-11-07 08:57:05', '', 84, 'http://ubti.zetalight.com/?page_id=296', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(299, 1, '2015-08-06 10:11:43', '2015-08-06 10:11:43', 'The Capstone Supplier Performance Module is a top-of-the-line, industry-tested supplier performance assessment framework with a built-in automated workflow and approval process. This module provides uniformity and consistency in the quality and scope of supplier assessments so you can reliably benchmark your suppliers. Capstone Supplier Performance provides on-demand access to supplier metrics across your enterprise, providing 360-degree feedback on supplier performance so you can:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Avoid surprises when suppliers fail to perform</li>\r\n	<li>Take corrective actions on your own</li>\r\n	<li>Improve supplier collaboration so as to avoid future issues</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWith dynamic and customizable supplier performance trend analysis at your fingertips, you can make more informed supplier contracting decisions and effectively mitigate your supplier risk.\r\n\r\n<strong>Best in Class</strong>\r\n\r\nWhy risk your company’s reputation with substandard supplier evaluation technology? We have spent years fine-tuning and continuously improving Capstone Supplier Performance functionality and usability so that you can conveniently and confidently access supplier information that will assist you in making better decisions about which suppliers to use. The module measures the performance of virtually any category of supplier based on whatever measurement parameters are appropriate for that product or service. With our industry-tested, stable and reliable supplier evaluation framework, you will have the latest technology driving your supplier selection strategy so you can minimize wasted time and resources and protect your profit margins.\r\n\r\n<strong>Manage Supplier Risk with Insightful Metrics</strong>\r\n\r\nPoor performance by suppliers has a direct impact on the bottom line. One broken link in your supply chain can result in a major system failure to your customer. Organizations that hold themselves to the gold standard of supplier management make every effort to comply with AS9100 paragraph 7.4.1, which requires periodic reviews of supplier performance, followed up by appropriate actions to manage performance and mitigate supplier risk. Capstone Supplier Performance Module is the right tool for managing supplier risk because it provides you with real-time data on all key elements of supplier performance, whether the outsourced work is for design, development, manufacturing, services, hardware, or software.\r\n\r\n<strong>Make Informed Supplier Decisions</strong>\r\n\r\nCapstone Supplier Performance provides you with hard performance data for intelligently selecting your supplier partners, whether they provide consulting, hardware or software development services, staffing or full-rate production of deliverable items. To produce your products and services to satisfy your customers consistently, you need suppliers that will be strong strategic partners. The Capstone Supplier Performance framework brings logic and reason to your supplier selection process. It takes the guesswork out of the equation because it provides data gathering, trend analysis, and reporting of key supplier performance metrics so that you can make well-informed source selection decisions.\r\n\r\n<strong>Capstone Supplier Performance Module Highlights</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Accommodate all types of supplier work including design, development, production, hardware, software, logistics, operations, maintenance, research and services</li>\r\n	<li>Create assessment goals for easy tracking and management of supplier performance</li>\r\n	<li>Evaluate and approve performance using fully automated workflow functionality</li>\r\n	<li>Generate automated email notifications for pending assessments and approvals</li>\r\n	<li>Utilize and download a full complement of standard reports, with customized reports available based on client needs</li>\r\n	<li>Provide 360-degree feedback to rated suppliers</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Contact us today to <a href="#" style="text-decoration: underline;" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#myModal">learn more.</a></p>', 'Capstone Supplier Performance', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'capstone-supplier-performance', '', '', '2016-11-07 08:56:54', '2016-11-07 08:56:54', '', 84, 'http://ubti.zetalight.com/?page_id=299', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(301, 1, '2015-08-06 10:17:27', '2015-08-06 10:17:27', '<strong>Managing Alerts for Product Integrity and Authenticity</strong>\r\n\r\nThe Capstone Alert Management Module is an automated system that notifies targeted resources when specified conditions exist in a process or product that warrant attention or action. Actions may be triggered by a notification pertaining to a product reliability issue, pending parts obsolescence notification, an alert from the Government Industry Data Exchange Program (GIDEP), or a notification about a suspect counterfeit part from customers or regulatory agencies. Capstone Alert Management has an embedded system for analyzing the alerts, defining the needed actions to be taken, and provides full traceability into the procurement and usage of the subject product. Capstone tracks and records the resolutions implemented to mitigate any risks associated with the product in question.\r\n\r\n<strong>A Key Element in your Counterfeit Parts Prevention and Mitigation Program</strong>\r\n\r\nThe new industry standard for counterfeit parts prevention and control, SAE Standard AS5553, requires that contractors have a process for investigating and tracking suspect counterfeit parts procurement and usage. Capstone Alert Management provides a means to investigate the possible use of suspect counterfeit parts and provides closed-loop authentication of the questions “where procured” and “where used.” Capstone provides a fully traceable record of each investigation, thereby eliminating the need to recreate each investigation’s results in the event of a future inquiry by a customer or regulatory agency.\r\n\r\n<strong>Capstone Alert Management Documents Compliance</strong>\r\n\r\nNew mandates and regulations increasingly place responsibility for liability issues squarely on the shoulders of the contractor and suppliers. Capstone facilitates compliance with detailed documentation of workflows, alerts, responses, and outcomes. Capstone also provides tiered, role-based reports with various levels of detail by simply clicking a button.\r\n\r\n<strong>Capstone Alert Management Module Highlights</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Role-based dashboards and alerts</li>\r\n	<li>Workflows to enforce accountability</li>\r\n	<li>Direct dissemination of alerts to groups based on their likelihood of usage</li>\r\n	<li>Compatibility with GIDEP alert format</li>\r\n	<li>Assigns action items to recipients</li>\r\n	<li>Logs responses to actions</li>\r\n	<li>Searchable records show actions and responses</li>\r\n	<li>Audit trail and reporting</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Contact us today to <a href="#" style="text-decoration: underline;" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#myModal">learn more.</a></p>', 'Capstone Alert Management', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'capstone-alert-management', '', '', '2016-11-07 08:57:23', '2016-11-07 08:57:23', '', 84, 'http://ubti.zetalight.com/?page_id=301', 0, 'page', '', 0),
