(512, 1, '2015-09-14 12:54:12', '2015-09-14 12:54:12', '<div id="Div1" style="display:none;">\n<a id="Data_Developer"></a><strong>Data Developer</strong>\n<ul id="ulData_Developer">\n	<li>Candidate should have minimum 2 years’ experience in SQL server 2008 and above, MSBI suite ( SSRS, SSIS, SSAS)</li>\n	<li>Experience in Upgrade of SSIS / SQL to new version is desirable.</li>\n	<li>Excellent communication skill in English as they will be directly working with the Client overseas.</li>\n	<li>Strong organizational skills and ability to multi-task; ability to work in a collaborative fast paced environment.</li>\n	<li>Diagnoses, isolates, and implements remedies for system failures caused by errors in application code.</li>\n	<li>Experience in C#. Net framework is an added advantage.</li>\n</ul>\n<p  id="pData_Developer" style="text-align: right;"><a class="apply-job" href="http://ubti.zetalight.com/job-application/">Apply</a></p>\n</div>\n\n<div id="Div2" style="display:none;">\n<a id="wpf"></a><strong>WPF</strong>\n<ul>\n	<li>3-4 years of professional software engineering experience</li>\n	<li>Solid command of SQL Server backend systems.</li>\n	<li>WPF (XAML) programming (MVVM architecture pattern)</li>\n	<li>Experience in object-oriented programming using C# in .NET</li>\n	<li>Experience with the Microsoft Stack including knowledge in C#, WPF (XAML), ASP.NET, Visual Studio 2010, and SQL Server</li>\n	<li>Ability to design, analyze and modify programming systems including coding, testing, debugging and documenting work</li>\n	<li>Participation in the planning and estimation of development iterations with other SDLC leads</li>\n	<li>Exposure in customizing and extending UI controls like Tree View, Ribbon, Property Grid, WPF Grid etc.</li>\n	<li>Must understand Dependency Property System</li>\n	<li>Must understand the underlying Threading model and the use of Dispatcher class</li>\n	<li>experience/expertise in migrating winforms application to WPF application.</li>\n</ul>\n<p style="text-align: right;display:none;"><a class="apply-job" href="http://ubti.zetalight.com/job-application/">Apply</a></p>\n</div>\n\n<div id="Div3" style="display:none;">\n<a id="wcf"></a><strong>WCF</strong>\n<ul>\n	<li>Candidate should have minimum 3 years’ experience with C#.Net framework, Web services, WCF, XSLT, CSS, JQuery, XML &amp; SQL Server</li>\n	<li>Good debugging skill in JQuery, .Net &amp; SQL server</li>\n	<li>Excellent communication skill</li>\n	<li>Strong organizational skills and ability to multi-task; ability to work in a collaborative fast paced environment.</li>\n	<li>Diagnoses, isolates, and implements remedies for system failures caused by errors in application code.</li>\n	<li>Ability to design, analyze and modify programming systems including coding, testing, debugging and documenting work</li>\n</ul>\n<p style="text-align: right;"><a class="apply-job" href="http://ubti.zetalight.com/job-application/">Apply</a></p>\n</div>\n<div id="Div4" style="display:none;">\n<a id="mvc"></a><strong>MVC</strong>\n<ul>\n	<li>Candidate should have minimum 3 years’ experience with C#.Net framework, SQL server 2008 & above MVC, Entity Framework, nTier architecture, Javascript, Jquery, HTML.</li>\n	<li>Good debugging skill in JQuery, .Net &amp; SQL server</li>\n	<li>Excellent communication skill</li>\n	<li>Strong organizational skills and ability to multi-task; ability to work in a collaborative fast paced environment.</li>\n	<li>Diagnoses, isolates, and implements remedies for system failures caused by errors in application code.</li>\n	<li>Ability to design, analyze and modify programming systems including coding, testing, debugging and documenting work</li>\n</ul>\n<p style="text-align: right;"><a class="apply-job" href="http://ubti.zetalight.com/job-application/">Apply</a></p>\n</div>\n\n<script type="text/javascript">\nShowHideMenubasedonURL();\nfunction ShowHideMenubasedonURL()\n{\nvar qrStr = window.location.search;\n    qrStr = qrStr.split("