(1257, 1, '2016-11-07 07:36:16', '2016-11-07 07:36:16', '<div class="banner">\r\n    <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-12"  style="padding-top: 20px;"> <a href="http://ubti.brmdevsite.com/industries/aerospace-and-defense"><img class="solu-image" src="http://ubti.brmdevsite.com/content/uploads/2016/11/aerospace_1.png"  /></a>\r\n      <h2><a href="http://ubti.brmdevsite.com/industries/aerospace-and-defense">AEROSPACE</a></h2>\r\n      <p>manufacturing | supply chain</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-12"  style="padding-top: 20px;"> <a href="http://ubti.brmdevsite.com/industries/financial-services/"><img class="solu-image" src="http://ubti.brmdevsite.com/content/uploads/2016/11/finance1.png"  /> </a>\r\n      <h2><a href="http://ubti.brmdevsite.com/industries/financial-services/">FINANCE</a></h2>\r\n      <p>asset management | banking </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-12"  style="padding-top: 20px;"> <a href="http://ubti.brmdevsite.com/industries/healthcare/"><img class="solu-image" src="http://ubti.brmdevsite.com/content/uploads/2016/11/health1.png"  /> </a>\r\n      <h2><a href="http://ubti.brmdevsite.com/industries/healthcare/">HEALTHCARE</a></h2>\r\n      <p style="line-height:18px;">health plans | providers <br/>\r\n        hospitals</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-12"  style="padding-top: 20px;"> <a href="http://ubti.brmdevsite.com/industries/other-industries/"><img class="solu-image" src="http://ubti.brmdevsite.com/content/uploads/2016/11/other_ind1.png" /></a>\r\n      <h2><a href="http://ubti.brmdevsite.com/industries/other-industries/">OTHER INDUSTRIES</a></h2>\r\n      <p style="line-height:18px;">government | education <br/>\r\n        insurance | more</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div style=" clear:both;"> </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n<div class="col-md-9 col-sm-12 ubt_con"><p>UB Technology Innovations, Inc. (UBTI) provides software and technology solutions to the aerospace, finance, and healthcare industries, among others. Our experienced team integrates and enhances your existing system so you can see the information you need it. These improved effciencies help you innovate, modernize, and succeed. </p>\r\n\r\n<p>UBTI has been serving clients since 1996 and has offices in the United States and Asia Pacific. Through a combination of experience, client focus, and innovation, we can become your trusted technology partner that provides solutions for improving effciency and increasing profitability. </p>\r\n	\r\n	', 'homefront', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'homefront', '', '', '2017-02-09 06:18:12', '2017-02-09 06:18:12', '', 0, 'http://ubti.brmdevsite.com/?page_id=1257', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(1262, 1, '2016-11-07 08:46:36', '2016-11-07 08:46:36', '<div class="strip"> government <img src="http://ubti.brmdevsite.com/content/uploads/2016/10/dot11.png" /> education <img src="http://ubti.brmdevsite.com/content/uploads/2016/10/dot11.png" /> insurance <img src="http://ubti.brmdevsite.com/content/uploads/2016/10/dot11.png" /> more </div>\r\n\r\n<img class="img-responsive" src="http://ubti.brmdevsite.com/content/uploads/2016/11/other_ban.png" width="100%" />\r\n\r\nUBTI has been making software smarter and more efficient for more than two decades, providing businesses with better visibility and access to their data. Our technology experts are available to deliver end-to-end solutions, or supplement internal resources on a project basis. We offer affordable, top-notch support whether we are working from our offices or yours. \r\n\r\n<p style="text-decoration:underline;"><strong>Industries we have served</strong></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class="ind_other">\r\n<div class="col-md-4">\r\n<ul>\r\n\r\n<li>Aerospace</li>\r\n<li>Asset management</li>\r\n<li>Banking</li>\r\n<li>Education</li>\r\n<li>Government</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="col-md-4">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Healthcare</li>\r\n<li>Insurance</li>\r\n<li>providers</li> \r\n<li>Scientific research</li>\r\n<li>… and more</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="clear:both;"></div>\r\n\r\n<br/>\r\n<p>Every industry has different requirements. That’s why UBTI offers a proven framework that can be extended to address your organization’s unique challenges. A few of our most popular solutions are below. </p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="row ser-block">\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class="col-md-4"><img src="http://ubti.brmdevsite.com/content/uploads/2016/04/development-home-icon.png"></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class="col-md-8">\r\n                <h4>CUSTOM DASHBOARDS</h4>\r\n                <p>Intuitive analytics dashboards with high level charts, action items, and reporting allow users to conveniently view data from multiple sou